                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/4932" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1261</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8393 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小土豆，大金豆 “姐弟俩”土豆粉战略定位及实施战略探索</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Little Potato, Big Golden Bean--Study on Strategic Orientation and Implementation Strategy of Sister-brother Catering Company</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">周修亭，王劭，刘永，梁玉巧</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">郑州大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">姐弟餐饮股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小微型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">姐弟俩土豆粉；发展战略；重新定位；利基型战略；平台型战略</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The sister and brother; potato flour noodles; development strategy ；strategic positioning;Repositioning；niche strategy; platform strategy </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">姐弟俩土豆粉是河南本地餐饮业的知名品牌，连锁店已经走出国门，开到了美国。掌舵人宋宝民的成长经历也是一个普通农民创业成功的典型案例。他把一个外地的小吃--土豆粉引进郑州，自发地依照“先发展后规范；边发展边规范”的战略思路，坚守着“产品是根，顾客是魂”的经营理念，经历了野蛮成长后的自我否定、自我革命，再到自我学习自我调整后的自我提升，探寻出了做某一品类的领先者的战略定位，经过1282次失败才得以成功的无明矾土豆粉专利技术，构建起了自己的核心竞争力，也增强了企业员工的凝聚力和战胜任何困难的信心。面对新冠疫情，他们冷静应对，众志成城，企业经营逆势上扬，为实现土豆粉类产品的国际冠军目标和下一步的平台化发展战略奠定了坚实的基础。该案例也为小微企业的发展战略提供了极有价值的经验借鉴</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The sister and brother potato flour noodles is a well-known brand in the Henan’s local catering industry. It has gone abroad and opened its chain stores in the United States. The growth experience of Song Baomin, the leader, is also a typical case of the success of ordinary farmers. He introduced an out-of-town snack, potato flour noodles, to Zhengzhou. After that, he spontaneously followed the strategic idea of ​​“development first, then standardization; development while standardization” and adhered to the business philosophy of “products are the roots, customers are the souls”. After experiencing the self-denial and self-revolution of extensive methods of economic growth, and then the self-improvement after self-learning and self-adjustment, he explored the strategic positioning of being a leader in a certain category. The patent technology of alum-free potato flour noodles, which was successful after 1282 failures, not only built the core competitiveness of the company, but also strengthened the cohesion of the employees and their confidence to overcome any difficulties. Facing the COVID-19, they work together and deal with it calmly. The enterprise rose against the trend, which laid a solid foundation not only for achieving the goal of becoming the international champion of potato flour noodles but also for the next platform of development strategy. This case also provides an extremely valuable experience for the development strategy of small and micro enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《市场营销》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">战略定位、品牌定位、重新定位、直营连锁、特许加盟、利基型战略和平台型</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
